'''Yang Fire Dog also known as дЄЩжИМ''' (hinoe inu, heikano inu, heijutsu) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еє≤жФѓ}}.

It is the 23rd combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Otsuy≈Н|ja|дєЩйЕЙ}} and the following combination is {{ill|Dinghai|ja|дЄБдЇ•}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and the Five Elements|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°М}}, the {{ill|Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤}}вАЩ {{ill|Bing|ja|дЄЩ}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|зБЂ}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|еНБдЇМжФѓ}}вАЩ {{ill|Dog|ja|жИМ}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|еЬЯ}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|зЫЄзФЯ}} (Fire produces Earth).

== Years of Bingu ==
A year in the {{ill|Common Era|ja|и•њжЪ¶}} that leaves a remainder of 26 when divided by 60 is a year of Bingu.
