== Months of Bingu ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|и•њжЪ¶}} year whose last digit is 0 or 5 (i.e. when the {{ill|Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤}} are either {{ill|Geng|ja|еЇЪ}} or {{ill|Yi|ja|дєЩ}}), the month of {{ill|September|ja|9жЬИ}} becomes the month of Bingu. However, here the term вАЬmonthвАЭ may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Old Lunar Calendar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|зЂЛжШ•}} until the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|еХУиЯД}}) as applicable.

== Days of Bingu ==
The [[Day Selection|selection]] for a Bingu day is as follows.
=== Day Selection ===
A Bingu day is the 3rd day of {{ill|Tenp≈Нkure|ja|еНБжЦєжЪЃ}}.

