== Months of Bingu ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|и•њжЪ¶}} year whose last digit is 0 or 5 (i.e. when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤}} are either {{ill|Geng|ja|еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)}} or {{ill|Yi|ja|дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)}}), the month of {{ill|September|ja|9жЬИ}} becomes the month of Bingu. However, here the term вАЬmonthвАЭ may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|зЂЛжШ•}} until the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|еХУиЯД}}) as applicable.

