It is the 23rd combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Otsuy≈Н|ja|дєЩйЕЙ|1=Yin Wood Rooster|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and the following combination is {{ill|Dinghai|ja|дЄБдЇ•|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°М|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}вАЩ {{ill|Bing|ja|дЄЩ|1=Hinoe (дЄЩ)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|зБЂ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|1=Earthly Branches|lt=Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|еНБдЇМжФѓ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}вАЩ {{ill|Dog|ja|жИМ|1=Dog (zodiac)|lt=Dog (жИМ)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|еЬЯ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|зЫЄзФЯ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Fire produces Earth).

