'''Yang Fire Dog also known as дЄЩжИМ''' (hinoe inu, heikano inu, heijutsu) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еє≤жФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.

It is the 23rd combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Otsuy≈Н|ja|дєЩйЕЙ|1=Yin Wood Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and the following combination is {{ill|Dinghai|ja|дЄБдЇ•|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°М|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}вАЩ {{ill|Bing|ja|дЄЩ|1=Hinoe (дЄЩ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|зБЂ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|1=Earthly Branches|lt=Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|еНБдЇМжФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}вАЩ {{ill|Dog|ja|жИМ|1=Dog (zodiac)|lt=Dog (жИМ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|еЬЯ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|зЫЄзФЯ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (Fire produces Earth).

