== Months of Bingu ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|и•њжЪ¶|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=и•њжЪ¶|4=zh|5=еЕђеЕГ|6=es|7=Era com√Їn|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} year whose last digit is 0 or 5 (i.e. when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} are either {{ill|Geng|ja|еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Yi|ja|дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|September|ja|9жЬИ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} becomes the month of Bingu. However, here the term вАЬmonthвАЭ may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|зЂЛжШ•|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|еХУиЯД|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) as applicable.

