'''Yang Fire Dog also known as дЄЩжИМ''' (hinoe inu, heikano inu, heijutsu) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еє≤жФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

It is the 23rd combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Otsuy≈Н|ja|1=Yin Wood Rooster|2=ja|дєЩйЕЙ|1=Yin Wood Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsuy≈Н|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Rooster|qq=}} and the following combination is {{ill|Dinghai|ja|1=Yin Fire Pig|2=ja|дЄБдЇ•|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dinghai|qq=}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°М|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}}вАЩ {{ill|Bing|ja|дЄЩ|1=Hinoe (дЄЩ)|lt=Hinoe (дЄЩ)|2=ja|3=дЄЩ|4=zh|5=дЄЩ|1=Hinoe (дЄЩ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (дЄЩ)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Fire|ja|зБЂ|1=Fire (wuxing)|lt=Fire (зБЂ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fire|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|1=Earthly Branches|lt=Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|еНБдЇМжФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Twelve Earthly Branches|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}}вАЩ {{ill|Dog|ja|жИМ|1=Dog (Zodiac)|lt=Dog (жИМ)|2=ja|3=жИМ|1=Dog (zodiac)|lt=Dog (жИМ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dog|13=User:Immanuelle/Dog (zodiac)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|Earth (еЬЯ)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (еЬЯ)|2=ru|3=–Ч–µ–Љ–ї—П (—Г-—Б–Є–љ)|4=mn|5=–®–Њ—А–Њ–Њ (–Љ–∞—Е–±–Њ–і)|6=uk|7=–Ч–µ–Љ–ї—П (–£-—Б—Ц–љ)|8=als|9=√Дrde in dr chinesische F√Љmf-Elem√§nt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=ThбїХ (Ng≈© h√†nh)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (еЬЯ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|qq=}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|зЫЄзФЯ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=}} (Fire produces Earth).

