Dog|ja|жИМ|1=Dog (Zodiac)|lt=Dog (жИМ)|2=ja|3=жИМ|1=Dog (zodiac)|lt=Dog (жИМ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dog|13=User:Immanuelle/Dog (zodiac)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dog|13=User:Immanuelle/Dog (Zodiac)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|Earth (еЬЯ)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (еЬЯ)|2=ru|3=–Ч–µ–Љ–ї—П (—Г-—Б–Є–љ)|4=mn|5=–®–Њ—А–Њ–Њ (–Љ–∞—Е–±–Њ–і)|6=uk|7=–Ч–µ–Љ–ї—П (–£-—Б—Ц–љ)|8=als|9=√Дrde in dr chinesische F√Љmf-Elem√§nt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=ThбїХ (Ng≈© h√†nh)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (еЬЯ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth (wuxing)|qq=}}, and they interact by {{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|зЫЄзФЯ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=}} (Fire produces Earth).

