== Months of Bingu ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|и•њжЪ¶|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=и•њжЪ¶|4=zh|5=еЕђеЕГ|6=es|7=Era com√Їn|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose last digit is 0 or 5 (i.e. when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are either {{ill|Geng|ja|еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|lt=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|2=ja|3=еЇЪ|4=zh|5=еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=}} or {{ill|Yi|ja|дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)|lt=Kinoto (дєЩ)|2=ja|3=дєЩ|4=zh|5=дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yi|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yi|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|September|ja|9жЬИ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September|qq=}} becomes the month of Bingu. However, here the term вАЬmonthвАЭ may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|зЂЛжШ•|1=Lichun|lt=Risshun|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Risshun|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Risshun|13=User:Immanuelle/Lichun|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|еХУиЯД|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichitsu|qq=}}) as applicable.

== Days of Bingu ==
The [[Day Selection|selection]] for a Bingu day is as follows.
=== Day Selection ===
A Bingu day is the 3rd day of {{ill|Tenp≈Нkure|ja|еНБжЦєжЪЃ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenp≈Нkure|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenp≈Нkure|qq=}}.
