∞—Е–±–Њ–і)|6=uk|7=–Ч–µ–Љ–ї—П (–£-—Б—Ц–љ)|8=als|9=√Дrde in dr chinesische F√Љmf-Elem√§nt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=ThбїХ (Ng≈© h√†nh)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (еЬЯ)|2=ru|3=–Ч–µ–Љ–ї—П (—Г-—Б–Є–љ)|4=mn|5=–®–Њ—А–Њ–Њ (–Љ–∞—Е–±–Њ–і)|6=uk|7=–Ч–µ–Љ–ї—П (–£-—Б—Ц–љ)|8=als|9=√Дrde in dr chinesische F√Љmf-Elem√§nt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=ThбїХ (Ng≈© h√†nh)|lt=Earth (еЬЯ)|qq=}}, and they interact by [[:en:Aioi|Mutual Generation]] (Fire produces Earth).
