eptember|September]] becomes the month of Bingu. However, here the term вАЬmonthвАЭ may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from [[:en:Lichun|Risshun]] until the day before [[:en:Jingzhe|Keichitsu]]) as applicable. ==Days of Yang Fire Dog== == Days of Bingu == The [[Day Selection|selection]] for a Bingu day is as follows. === Day Selection === A Bingu day is the 3rd day of {{ill|Tenp≈Нkure|ja|еНБжЦєжЪЃ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenp≈Нkure|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenp≈Нkure|qq=}}. == See Also == * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
