== Months of Bingu == In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose last digit is 0 or 5 (i.e. when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Ten Heavenly Stems]] are either {{ill|Geng|ja|еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|lt=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|2=ja|3=еЇЪ|4=zh|5=еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=}} or {{ill|Yi|ja|дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)|lt=Kinoto (дєЩ)|2=ja|3=дєЩ|4=zh|5=дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yi|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yi|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:September|September]] becomes the month of Bingu. However, here the term вАЬmonthвАЭ may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from [[:en:Lichun|Risshun]] until the day before [[:en:Jingzhe|Keichitsu]]) as applicable.
